781
02:01:26,343 --> 02:01:28,408
No...

782
02:01:28,409 --> 02:01:30,474
No!

783
02:01:36,744 --> 02:01:38,787
No! No!

784
02:01:39,710 --> 02:01:42,800
Non ti amo più! Non ti amo più!

